---
description: Go source conventions
globs:
  - "**/*.go"
  - "!**/*_test.go"
---
When editing Go source files in this repository:

- Follow `gofmt` style; run `gofmt -l .` before finishing.
- Keep imports organized; group standard library, then third-party, then internal.
- Preserve domain terms: `UEFI`, `GPT`, `SHA-256`, `PGP`.
- Add lowercase why-focused comments for non-obvious logic.
- Match existing package conventions in the same directory.
